  "{\n  \"Situation_ID\": \"S1\",\n  \"Situation_Name\": \"Trend: Anti-ageing Skincare for Gen Z\",\n  \"Description\": \"Gen Z is seeking anti-ageing skincare products that promote longevity in a preventative approach to ageing. Hashtags like #CollagenBoosting indicate a shift towards younger generations embracing anti-ageing routines.\",\n  \"Key_Contextual_Factors\": [\"Preventative approach to ageing\", \"Embracing anti-ageing at a younger age\"],\n  \"Associated_Problem_Or_Opportunity\": \"Meeting the demand for anti-ageing skincare products among younger consumers.\",\n  \"Frequency_Or_Commonality_Indication\": \"Growing trend among Gen Z consumers.\",\n  \"Source_Document_Reference\": \"Prejuventation and Future of Skincare 2027 forecasts\",\n  \"Evidence_Snippets\": [\"Gen Z is looking to anti-ageing formulations that promote longevity in a preventative approach to ageing.\", \"Hashtags like #CollagenBoosting hold a 'very long' lifespan, showcasing how anti-ageing approaches are no longer just for older generations.\"],\n  \"Keywords\": [\"Anti-ageing skincare\", \"Gen Z\", \"Preventative approach\", \"Collagen boosting\"]\n}",
